title: 'collator-protocol revamp: Increase channel size used by the background writer
  of `PersistentDb`'
doc:
- audience: Node Dev
  description: |-
    Increases the channel capacity used by `PersistentDb` and `PeerManager` to avoid delaying
    `PersistenceRequests` in spam scenarios.
    Introduce a separate log target for the persistent_db module.
crates:
- name: polkadot-collator-protocol
  bump: patch
